hotels.title: Hôtel d'Orsay Paris 7ème - Esprit de France
hotels.info: A stone's throw from the Musée d'Orsay and the Quais de Seine.

hotels.title: Hôtel Jacques de Molay
hotels.info: A boutique hotel situated in a beautiful building of the Marais district in Paris

hotels.title: Cadet Residence (appart hôtel Paris 9)
hotels.info: CADET Residence in the centre of Paris offers large apartments for unforgettable short-term rentals in Paris! They are indeed spacious apartments, with colorful decoration, fitted out as living spaces to stay with family or friends (for 2 to 6 people).

hotels.title: Hôtel Villa Glamour
hotels.info: Nestled in the heart of the 16th arrondissement, a few steps from the most emblematic tourist sites (Trocadéro, Eiffel Tower), major sporting events (Parc des Princes, Roland Garros), and business locations (OECD, the 16th century Town Hall, Le Pavillon Royal…), the Villa Glamour welcomes you in a former private residence from the Napoleon III period transformed into a romantic and elegant private mansion.

hotels.title: Les Patios du Marais
hotels.info: A wide variety of apartments, accessible by stairs, with exposed beams and stones and in a green setting, rare in Paris, in six buildings of 18th and 19th centuries, the whole forming a private passage.

hotels.title: Hôtel Moderniste
hotels.info: Located in a beautiful and very quiet bourgeois street in the 15th arrondissement of Paris, in the heart of the Convention district and very close to the Porte de Versailles Exhibition Center, the Hotel Moderniste opens its doors after a 2 years complete renovation.

hotels.title: HotelHome Paris 16
hotels.info: In the heart of the 16th arrondissement, this guest house is the ideal solution for spending a few days in Paris enjoying the advantages of a fully equipped apartment.

hotels.title: Shangri-la Hotel Paris
hotels.info: In the former home of Prince Roland Bonaparte, overlooking the Eiffel Tower and River Seine in the 16th arrondissement, ultimate Parisian elegance lives on at Shangri-La Paris. Holding both Palace distinction and Monument Historique status, the hotel seamlessly blends European grandeur with traditional Asian hospitality and is home to the only Michelin-starred Chinese restaurant in France.

hotels.title: Hôtel Plaza Athénée
hotels.info: Sleep peacefully in beautiful rooms, surrounded by Parisian splendour and our famous art of hospitality.

hotels.title: Arty Paris Porte de Versailles By River
hotels.info: Completely renovated and decorated, every detail of the hostel has been combed to create an ultra-modern, elegant and trendy design. Spacious and bright, with large windows and phrases flocked on the walls the hostel will gives you the impression of being in an artist’s loft.

hotels.title: Atypik Hôtel
hotels.info: The ATYPIK hotel is a singular boutique hotel, created at the intersection between the industrial past and the cosmopolitan present of Clichy.

hotels.title: Excelsior République
hotels.info: The proximity of metro line 3, direct to Opera or Saint Lazare station and its department stores (including Galeries Lafayette) make this hotel an ideal place for a typical Parisian stay.

hotels.title: Meininger Hotel Paris Porte de Vincennes
hotels.info: Heure d'arrivée : 15:00

hotels.title: Grand Hôtel des Gobelins
hotels.info: Cosy atmosphere, family hotel, the Grand Hotel des Gobelins will meet your expectations.The team will welcome you and advise whatever you will need.They will give you all the good addresses in the area (restaurants, museum, walks…in the nearby). They are close to Jardin des Plantes, Latin Quarter, Mouffetard Market, Jardin du Luxembourg.

hotels.title: Hôtel HOY
hotels.info: Their spaces have been created as sanctuaries to promote healthy habits in each room, enhancing your well-being.

hotels.title: Hôtel Terre Neuve
hotels.address: 22 bis Rue de Terre Neuve, 75020 Paris
hotels.info: Terre Neuve hotel is offering you a journey in an authentically parisan and lively district of the capital, while offering a convenient access to the rest of the city, thanks to public transportation around the hotel. Discover a bohemian district where individual houses, trendy restaurants and bars mingle.

hotels.title: Hôtel Romance Malesherbes by Patrick Hayat
hotels.info: The Hotel Romance Malesherbes is ideally located in a quiet street of the very stylish 17th district of Paris. You are at walking distance from the famous department stores “Grands Magasins”, the Opera, the Champs Elysées or Montmartre, as well as the splendid Parc Monceau.`

hotels.title: Hôtel du Théâtre by Patrick Hayat
hotels.info: Located in a quiet street of the upscale 17th district of Paris, the Hotel du Théâtre owes its name from the lovely Hébertot theatre situated just across the street

hotels.title: Hôtel Mercure Paris Tour Eiffel Pont Mirabeau
hotels.info: Mercure Paris Tour Eiffel Pont Mirabeau is a 4-star hotel in downtown Paris overlooking the Seine and close to the Eiffel Tower.

hotels.title: Hôtel Charles V
hotels.info: Located on the site of the former royal residence called Hôtel Saint-Pol, home of Charles V and his relatives, our 4-star hotel invites you to discover the many facets of the Marais district and the Village Saint-Paul with its antique shops, designer boutiques, small courtyards and authentic charm.

hotels.title: Les Clés Du 27 Paris
hotels.info: The Appart Hotel is the independence and comfort of home, with hotel services in addition! An appart hotel is a furnished tourist accommodation with hotel-like services and where very short term rentals are possible.

hotels.title: Mama Shelter Paris East
hotels.info: Heure d'arrivée : 15:00

hotels.title: The Ritz Paris
hotels.info: Whichever option you choose at the Ritz Paris, you'll find a cachet you won't find elsewhere. Overlooking the rooftops of Paris or our charming Grand Jardin, the details and décor breathe style and spirit. What do the French call it? Je ne sais quoi.

hotels.title: Camping de Paris
hotels.address: 2 All. du Bord de l'Eau, 75016 Paris
hotels.info: Camp in the very heart of Paris, on the banks of the Seine in the midst of nature! Set in the heart of the 16th arrondissement, Paris campsite**** is ideally located for exploring Paris and its emblematic monuments. Take the shuttle bus from the campsite to reach Porte Maillot metro station in just a few minutes.

hotels.title: Hôtel du Mont Blanc Paris
hotels.info: Located in the heart of the Latin Quarter, the Hotel Mont Blanc is a modern establishment ideal for exploring Paris: you will be less than 15 minutes on foot from emblematic sites such as Notre-Dame Cathedral, the Luxembourg Gardens, the Pantheon, Saint-Germain-des-Prés church, Place Saint Michel and the Louvre Museum.
